<br>
First of all, I want to try and get everyone involved.  Even sub level 50's have been doing this area.  So I think the level cut off will be 48 for the moment.<br>
<br>
Second, I have been making waiting lists for folks when there is an open spot.  This list is based purely on need, you may be at the top of the list, but if I need a healer and you are a tank you will have to wait.<br>
<br>
Lastly, if you can learn the area I will be more inclined to ask you to visit this camp (hint, hint).<br>
<br>
I got a parchment, a stack of Blue Diamonds and other various cash loot from PoJ.  Oh and did I mention EXP up the wazzooo.  Alpha loot on cash drops, rolls on Blue Diamonds and polearms.  I do not consider this to be a guild function so guild rolls do not apply.  I have not made up my mind on parchment drops as of yet (Do warriors/rogues get to roll?).<br>
<br>
